The evidence with the title 'Air Force One - Wikipedia ' says Air Force One is the official air traffic control call sign for a United States Air Force aircraft carrying the president of the United States . In common parlance the term describes those Air Force aircraft designed , built, and used to transport the president . The presidential aircraft is a prominent symbol of the American presidency  ... . Eisenhower became the first president to use the VC-137 during his " Flight To  ... 
